{
  "texts": [
    "For each criterion, the experts were asked to rate the generated TS according to the five criteria based on the Likert scale and also verbalize their rationale for a given choice to ensure that they had a consistent understanding of each rating scale.",
    "The experts were free to provide individual ratings in the interview survey.",
    "However, in most cases, they all agreed on the same rating.",
    "In case, they gave a rating of 1, i.e., Strongly Disagree on Relevance, Coverage or Correctness for any TS, we did not proceed with the remaining criteria.",
    "Subsequently, we asked the experts to answer Feasibility based on the premise that the issues have been addressed."
  ]
}